high_descs: go in the kitchen and approach the counter where the coffee pot is sitting
remove the mug from the coffee machine
take the mug to the stove and raise toward the microwave
warm the mug in the microwave then remove it
walk the heated mug back to the counter where the coffee machine is
place the cup back under the machines dispenser
anns.task_desc: take a mug from the coffee machine, warm it in the microwave, then put it back under the machines dispenser

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to the refrigerator, then turn left and go to the counter across from you where the coffee maker is.
Pick up the white coffee mug, in the coffee maker.
Move to the microwave above the stove, directly to your left.
Place the coffee mug in the microwave, warm it up, then remove the coffee mug from the microwave.
Turn to your right and go back to the coffee maker.
Put the white coffee mug back in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm coffee mug in the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the fridge, then turn left and go to the coffee maker.
Move to the left to the microwave.
Heat the mug in the microwave.
Put the mug on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug on the coffee maker.
